![UI Preview](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1451/685/menu-and-pop-up-png-png.png)

---

## Usage

To open the configuration panel and assign your talent loadouts to specific contexts, use either of the following slash commands:

* `/ats`
* `/ascensiontalents`

---

## Installation

1. Download the latest release.
2. Extract the AscensionTalentManager folder into your World of Warcraft/_retail_/Interface/AddOns directory.
3. Restart the game or reload your UI (/reload).

